description: Unable to register this HPE OneView instance with iLO: Unable to establish trusted communication with the server..

eventDetails.eventItemValue: Ensure network connectivity to the iLO is available, reset the iLO using iLO web interface, wait for iLO to restart and refresh the server. If the problem persists, power cycle the server, wait for the server to complete Power On Self-Test (POST) and then refresh the server. If there are any active alerts for the server that are related to certificate based communication with the iLO, resolve the issue as per the resolution steps  provided in the alert and retry the operation.
